Better

I wanted life to be better, 
so I decided to be happy with what I had, 
to give even when I had little, 
to love when I was afraid, 
to forgive even if it was not asked for, 
and to shed worry, anxiety, and regret.  
I did these things, 
and life was better.

Midnight musings by
Tammi Brown Keech
2021
